# Instagram API Configuration
# Get your access token from: https://developers.facebook.com/apps/
# See INSTAGRAM_SETUP.md for detailed instructions

# Required - Instagram Access Token (long-lived, valid for 60 days)
INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_instagram_token_here

# Optional - Date of last token refresh (automatic check every 30 days)
# Format: YYYY-MM-DD
# Example: INSTAGRAM_TOKEN_LAST_REFRESH=2026-01-26
INSTAGRAM_TOKEN_LAST_REFRESH=

# ============================================================================
# GITHUB PAGES DEPLOYMENT
# Zobacz: GITHUB_PAGES_SETUP.md
# ============================================================================

# Local development:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN with your real token
# 3. Run: npm run build

# GitHub Pages (Production):
# 1. Add INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN to GitHub Secrets (Settings → Secrets → Actions)
# 2. Add PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN to GitHub Secrets (for auto token refresh)
# 3. Push to GitHub → auto deploy!

